  "root_text": {
    "iti80:0.1": "Itivuttaka 80 ",
    "iti80:0.2": "Tikanipāta ",
    "iti80:0.3": "Catutthavagga ",
    "iti80:0.4": "Vitakkasutta ",
    "iti80:1.1": "Vuttañhetaṁ bhagavatā vuttamarahatāti me sutaṁ: ",
    "iti80:2.1": "“Tayome, bhikkhave, akusalavitakkā. ",
    "iti80:2.2": "Katame tayo? ",
    "iti80:2.3": "Anavaññattipaṭisaṁyutto vitakko, lābhasakkārasilokapaṭisaṁyutto vitakko, parānuddayatāpaṭisaṁyutto vitakko. ",
    "iti80:2.4": "Ime kho, bhikkhave, tayo akusalavitakkā”ti. ",
    "iti80:2.5": "Etamatthaṁ bhagavā avoca. ",
    "iti80:2.6": "Tatthetaṁ iti vuccati: ",
    "iti80:3.1": "“Anavaññattisaṁyutto, ",
    "iti80:3.2": "lābhasakkāragāravo; ",
    "iti80:3.3": "Sahanandī amaccehi, ",
    "iti80:3.4": "ārā saṁyojanakkhayā. ",
    "iti80:4.1": "Yo ca puttapasuṁ hitvā, ",
    "iti80:4.2": "Vivāhe saṁharāni ca; ",
    "iti80:4.3": "Bhabbo so tādiso bhikkhu, ",
    "iti80:4.4": "Phuṭṭhuṁ sambodhimuttaman”ti. ",
    "iti80:5.1": "Ayampi attho vutto bhagavatā, iti me sutanti. ",
    "iti80:5.2": "Paṭhamaṁ. "
  },
  "translation_text": {
    "iti80:0.1": "So It Was Said 80 ",
    "iti80:0.2": "The Book of the Threes ",
    "iti80:0.3": "Chapter Four ",
    "iti80:0.4": "Thoughts ",
    "iti80:1.1": "This was said by the Buddha, the Perfected One: that is what I heard. ",
    "iti80:2.1": "“Mendicants, there are these three unskillful thoughts. ",
    "iti80:2.2": "What three? ",
    "iti80:2.3": "The thought of status; of getting material things, honor, and popularity; and of fondness for others. ",
    "iti80:2.4": "These are the three unskillful thoughts.” ",
    "iti80:2.5": "The Buddha spoke this matter. ",
    "iti80:2.6": "On this it is said: ",
    "iti80:3.1": "“One concerned with being looked up to, ",
    "iti80:3.2": "with possessions, honor, and respect, ",
    "iti80:3.3": "with sharing joys with friends, ",
    "iti80:3.4": "is far from the ending of fetters. ",
    "iti80:4.1": "But one who gives up children and herds, ",
    "iti80:4.2": "marriage and acquisitions—",
    "iti80:4.3": "such a mendicant is capable ",
    "iti80:4.4": "of experiencing the highest awakening.” ",
    "iti80:5.1": "This too is a matter that was spoken by the Blessed One: that is what I heard. "
  },
